Getting started with API/SDK

This page serves as an Everscale API and SDK starting point. It offers guidance on all necessary information, instructions and instruments needed to prooceed with launching your own DApp. 

The Everscale API is provided by GraphQL Server. It provides applications the connection to an Everscale node that is part of the Everscale network. Developers are able to access on-chain data and process transactions on the network by making use of the endpoints provided by the Everscale API. Please follow this link for a complete API guidance - ссылка на апи

The Everscale SDK is supported for 14 programming languages for all the popular platforms. It helps developers to create messages, handle network issues and implement any possible use-case. Please follow this link for a complete SDK guidance - ссылка на сдк
